					"value": "A dwarf and a gnome from the Lower City are food shopping in wyrm's crossing. The gnome is panic shopping, convinced there is going to be siege, shortages, etc. (Very covid buying all the toilet paper it's a doomsday kind of vibe). Her dwarven girlfriend is doing her best to reign her in, while also trying to be understanding."
